&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Hands of clock coincides 11 times in 12 hours.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

