&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;The hands overlap about every 65 minutes, not every 60 minutes. The hands coincide 22 times in a day.&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;In Next 12 Hours&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: var(--bs-body-font-family); font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);&quot;&gt;Hands of clock coincides 11 times.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: var(--bs-body-font-family); font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);&quot;&gt;So, hands of clocks coincide 33 times in 36 Hours.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: var(--bs-body-font-family); font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);&quot;&gt;Hence, the correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: var(--bs-body-font-family); font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align); font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;33&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: var(--bs-body-font-family); font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight);&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>उपरोक्त प्रश्न का सही उत्तर विकल्प 4 है। हम जल्द ही विस्तृत समाधान अपडेट करेंगे।

&lt;p&gt;While using the formula:&lt;/p&gt;

